snippet.title: I Expect You To Die 3 | Gameplay Trailer | Meta Quest 2 + 3 + Pro
snippet.description:
I Expect You To Die 3: Cog in the Machine is launching on Meta Quest in Summer 2023. Pre-order today: https://metaque.st/45kpFJL 

Meet Dr. Roxana Prism, a brilliant scientist and former Agency inventor, who believes she can create a better agent, one that’s superior to humans. And she has it out for you, Agent. Your mission: stay alive long enough to defeat this new escalating threat.
